\c 12
\s Rwiyo rwokuvonga
\p
\v 1 Nezuva iro uchati, "Ndinokuvongai Jehovha; makanga makandi tsamwira, asi kutsamwa kwenyu kwakadzorwa, munondinyaradza.
\v 2 Tarirai, Mwari ndiye ruponeso rwangu; ndichavimba naye, handingatyi; nokuti Jehovha, iye Jehovha, ndiye simba rangu norwiyo rwangu; iye wava ruponeso rwangu."
\v 3 Saka muchachera mvura nomufaro pamatsime oruponeso.
\p
\v 4 Zvino nezuva iro muchati, "Vongai Jehovha, paridzai zita rake, zivisai mabasa ake pakati pavanhu, muudze vanhu kuti zita rake rinokudziwa.
\p
\v 5 "Imbirai Jehovha; nokuti akaita zvinhu zvakaisvonaka-naka; izvi ngazvizikanwe panyika yose.
\v 6 Danidzira upururudze, iwe ugere paZioni; nokuti Mutsvene waIsiraeri mukuru pakati penyu."
